      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GENERAL FRED (5) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (22.64) at Geelong. Strike-rate solid and expected to feature in the finish. LET'S WIN BINGO (2) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (20.12) at Traralgon over 350m. Well-placed to take this out. DON'T CONFESS (1) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (22.85) at this track. Key player if finds best. CAN'T TURN LEFT (4) makes debut for the Laurence Scala kennel. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
